    <string name="privacy_policy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_content">
        EchoGuard Privacy Policy\n\n
        
        EchoGuard is designed to protect your privacy by monitoring how other apps use permissions on your device.\n\n
        
        Data Collection:\n
        • EchoGuard only collects permission usage data locally on your device\n
        • No personal data is transmitted to external servers\n
        • All data is encrypted using Android Keystore\n\n
        
        Data Usage:\n
        • Permission access logs are used to generate privacy scores and alerts\n
        • App information is used to assess risk levels\n
        • Usage statistics help identify potential privacy violations\n\n
        
        Data Storage:\n
        • All data is stored locally on your device\n
        • You can export or delete your data at any time\n
        • Data retention period can be configured in settings\n\n
        
        Permissions:\n
        • Usage Access: Required to monitor app permission usage\n
        • Notification Access: Required for real-time monitoring\n
        • Package Query: Required to analyze installed apps\n\n
        
        Contact:\n
        For questions about this privacy policy, contact: privacy@echoguard.app
    </string>
